      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HERE NO CASH (1) steps out at this track for the first time after an average run at the latest appearance, finishing fourth at Gosford over 515m behind Code Of Silence (30.61). The form from her last run stacks up well. Has ability and is a key runner. FEDERAL ACE (5) spotted a start but wound up strongly late and finished second and beaten 2.25 lengths (18.76) at this track in Maiden. Good beginner but will need a little luck from a middle draw. Can measure up. SAID AND DONE (4) is a handily bred pup making her debut without a trial. Worth keeping a close eye on the market. OPTIMISM (7) is a Peter Lagogiane-trained newcomer by Tommy Shelby out of Pay Call. Start all important and will need some luck getting across from the wide draw. Can feature with the right run.",
